{"tid":1267641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張宇人：不贊成以獨立委員會調查反修例衝突","createTime":"2019-06-30T03:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T05:21:53.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a108453c70172ff50519ace65c9e586be48fcb","tid":1267641,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:53:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】身兼行政會議成員的自由黨主席張宇人表示，就逃犯條例修訂引起的爭議，政府應該做或可以做的已經做了，他又指基於法治，不可能特赦或承諾不檢控示威者，亦不贊成成立獨立調查委員會，調查反修例警民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n他又勸喻年輕人，遊行示威要理性表達意見，即使要表達訴求，又是否需要一而再、再而三地令政府部門工作停頓。對於行會連續兩星期取消會議，張宇人表示期間有傳閱及批准文件，不開會並非等同完全不做事。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353658&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=420bec9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353658&h=59840630\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353658</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cf3ed8ec3adddf57e1c288c58186b69b86f71f","tid":1267641,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"認住佢<br />\n飲食界張宇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c230cf14ead6b4d174ed0a8881b4a7d8b580f1ef","tid":1267641,"uid":40763,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"呢d撚樣 成個香港政府都有大撚把<br />\n醫管局 警狗 立法會 icac 教育局 港鐵<br />\n加埋政務司 財政司 律政司 特首<br />\n<br />\n成個香港都官官相衛 不撚知所謂"},{"pid":"88f0636d2caa85ddf81b038a5ff9cae701b0bba5","tid":1267641,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"特赦關法唔法治事？咁以前啲特赦又係點？"},{"pid":"df16404feab82ab2e04d376bd8e79fdde51a8b05","tid":1267641,"uid":34478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90cf3ed8ec3